{"tid":197204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發! 多蒙特隊巴爆炸，歐聯賽事取消","createTime":"2017-04-11T18:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T21:23:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c90909e3ad5766caaf0d4a133b04a0f1c95bca","tid":197204,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:14:51.000Z","msg":"An explosion has hit a bus carrying the Borussia Dortmund football team to a Champions League match, the club says.<br />\n<br />\nPlayer Marc Bartra has been injured and has been taken to hospital.<br />\n<br />\nNorth-Rhine Westphalia police said they were at the scene and there are reports that the fire service are also there.<br />\n<br />\nThe team tweeted (in German) that the other players were safe."},{"pid":"9ff0752acf83679de6fec7b76f9a4bd55caef138","tid":197204,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:15:29.000Z","msg":"多蒙特球隊的大巴在前往球場的路上遭遇爆炸襲擊，俱樂部官方證實大巴上有一人在這次事故中受傷，已經被送往醫院，根據《圖片報》得到的消息，受傷的是多蒙特後衞巴查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事發地在距離多蒙特的主場約有10公里的Wittbr&auml;ucker大街，事發現場散落了一地的碎玻璃。炸藥被事先埋在了街道上，在多蒙特大巴通過時發生了爆炸，警方正在調查這是否是一起針對性的襲擊。"},{"pid":"f0566c9d7fae6b4c53b46b9d9ba81e0f4f3267ac","tid":197204,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669f3f31d55cfc904b3b9bc5068080ab99d01bb8","tid":197204,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744ac730fc11325ffec7dd140e3d59ad672d819a","tid":197204,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.corriere.it/methode_image/2017/04/11/Sport/Foto%20Sport%20-%20Trattate/Clipboard-kq8H-U433001081395908djH-1224x916@Corriere-Web-Sezioni.jpg?v=20170411201602\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.corriere.it%2Fmethode_image%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2FSport%2FFoto%2520Sport%2520-%2520Trattate%2FClipboard-kq8H-U433001081395908djH-1224x916%40Corriere-Web-Sezioni.jpg%3Fv%3D20170411201602&h=7eaa4f03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c66fd3e9142021281f1013bb5f3a88c55db44a","tid":197204,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8dd29483d8535c9d5df48c598ed859b9eb66f4","tid":197204,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:24:26.000Z","msg":"邊位球迷"},{"pid":"18535c2e756d615307b3ea5aae0d95f9a0f5c2e5","tid":197204,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09805978f95b14d99d002c15d1fd7ebc6f116d6","tid":197204,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山!  多蒙特應該係法西斯"},{"pid":"561ae8d6596f75414c548e84351d910e8f850c63","tid":197204,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:26:27.000Z","msg":"According to Die Welt, Dortmund&rsquo;s team bus was damaged by not one but three explosions on Wittbr&auml;uckerstra&szlig;e, just over six miles from the Dortmund stadium. Reports suggest the damage was mainly to windows. The cause of the explosions are unknown."},{"pid":"31c0ad0ac6618e99