","msg":"踢場波都被人炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bd6dbfbf937d50f83fd792842ba6f970e83488","tid":197204,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝燒山!  多蒙特應該係法西斯</blockquote><br />\n發生呢啲事，第一時間應該關心穆斯林會唔會俾人屌先，佢地好慘架，仲慘過球員受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c28a6d294d8f6b7ab582ddb97be656527662f83","tid":197204,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝燒山!  多蒙特應該係法西斯</blockquote><br />\n發生呢啲事，第一時間應該關心穆斯林會唔會俾人屌先，佢地好慘架，仲慘過球員受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多仔自爆陷害穆斯林，簡直萬惡之首啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ba3472e5d9b6a330f78d1aa51c575c23c57f02","tid":197204,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"突發"},{"pid":"59f4484a80ce6c81c890b6c32855f9ae56cbd4fd","tid":197204,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:02:44.000Z","msg":"片"},{"pid":"3d18076bd48df3bb0a8453b0f4864862d92a7def","tid":197204,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eba5f9ab4dc0af0acc57beb24ac0cb38caccd4","tid":197204,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15d172f5775786fae0b78e14cf95013e0805a13a","tid":197204,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,